         <description>Eunice Paddio-Johnson was born on June 25, 1928, in Crowley, La. She
            graduated from Grambling State University in 1949 and taught in Saint Helena Parish,
            La., and at Cornell University in Ithaca, N.Y. She retired from teaching in 1972 and was
            elected to the Saint Helena Parish School Board.</description>
